  "description": "Extends the error code system beyond the 4 bus-validation codes (SOS-4001/2/3/4) shipped in v0.4.0. Adds SOS-5xxx (auth), SOS-6xxx (runtime / squad / bus-delivery), SOS-7xxx (economy / billing / settlement). Single exception class hierarchy at sos/contracts/errors.py with `.code`, `.message`, `.http_status`. Every HTTPException raised across services now carries a taxonomy code as a stable identifier for clients.",
